quran[9{c,v,t}:
42,23,"yeh hai woh cheez jis ki khush khaberi Allah apne unn bundon ko deta hai jinhon ne maan liya aur naik amal kiye ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn logon se keh do ke mein iss kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon, Albata qaraabat ki mohabbat zaroor chahta hon jo koi bhalai kamaye ga hum is ke liye is bhalai mein khoobi ka izafah kar den ge be shak Allah bara Dur guzar karne wala aur qader daan hai"
42,24,kya yeh log kehte hain ke iss shakhs ne Allah par jhoota bohtan ghurr liya hai? agar Allah chahay to tumahray dil par mohar kar day woh baatil ko mita deta hai aur haq ko apne farmanon se haq kar dekhata hai woh seenon ke chupay hue raaz jaanta hai
42,25,"wohi hai jo apne bundon se tauba qubool karta hai aur buraiyon se dar guzar karta hai, halaank tum logon ke sab af-aal ka aُ se ilm hai"
42,26,"woh imaan laane walon aur naik amal karne walon ki dua qubool karta hai aur apne fazl se un ko aur ziyada deta hai rahay inkaar karne walay, to un ke liye dard naak saza hai"
42,27,"agar Allah apne sab bundon ko khula rizaq day deta to woh zameen mein sar kashi ka tufaan barpaa kar dete, magar woh aik hisaab se jitna chahta hai nazil karta hai, yaqeenan woh apne bundon se ba khabar hai aur unn par nigah rakhta hai"
42,28,"wohi hai jo logon ke mayoos ho jaane ke baad meen brsata hai aur apni rehmat phela deta hai, aur wohi qabil tareef walii hai"
42,29,"uss ki nshanyon mein se hai yeh zameen aur asmano ki paidaiesh, aur yeh jandaar makhloqaat jo uss ne dono jagah phela rakhi hain woh jab chahay inhen akhatta kar sakta hai"
42,30,"tum par jo museebat bhi aayi hai, tumahray apne hathon ki kamaai se aayi hai, aur bohat seKasoroo-n se woh waisay hi Dur guzar kar jata hai"
42,31,"tum zameen mein apne khuda ko aajiz kar dainay walay nahi ho, aur Allah ke muqablay mein tum koi haami o nasir nahi rakhtay"
